headline.main: German Conservatives Edge Ahead of Social Democrats in Emnid Poll
headline.print_headline: German Conservatives Edge Ahead of Social Democrats in Emnid Poll

lead_paragraph: German Chancellor Angela Merkel's conservatives took a one point lead over the Social Democrats (SPD) in the latest poll conducted by Emnid for the German newspaper Bild am Sonntag, with nearly seven months to go before federal elections.
